---
const options = [
  {
    locale: 'pt',
    title: 'Português',
    description: 'Leituras sobre IA aplicada, engenharia de software, fundamentos, laboratórios e estudos de caso para continuar aprendendo com direção.',
    href: '/pt/',
    cta: 'Abrir edição em português',
    image: '/assets/images/desktop-5.webp',
  },
  {
    locale: 'en',
    title: 'English',
    description: 'Editorial coverage of software engineering, applied AI, practical guides, labs, and case studies for builders who want signal over noise.',
    href: '/en/',
    cta: 'Open English edition',
    image: '/assets/images/news-1.webp',
  },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
    <title>AI Engineering</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AI Engineering is a technology blog about software engineering, applied AI, practical guides, labs, and case studies in Portuguese and English."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light;
        --bg: #f4f8fa;
        --surface: #ffffff;
        --surface-soft: #eef4f6;
        --border: rgba(20, 44, 58, 0.1);
        --text: #13232c;
        --muted: #4b5d66;
        --accent: #117f81;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f7fafb 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      }

      main {
        width: min(1100px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 56px 0 72px;
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .hero {
        display: grid;
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 26px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--surface);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 48px rgba(20, 44, 58, 0.08);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 10ch;
        font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 5rem);
        line-height: 0.96;
      }

      .lede {
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 60ch;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
        font-size: 1.04rem;
      }

      .manifesto {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .manifesto div {
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .grid {
        margin-top: 28px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 20px;
      }

      .card {
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--surface);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(20, 44, 58, 0.06);
      }

      .card img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .copy {
        padding: 18px 20px 20px;
      }

      .card h2 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: 1.45rem;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .card a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 44px;
        padding: 0 16px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .footer-note {
        margin-top: 24px;
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);
        background: var(--surface-soft);
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      @media (max-width: 780px) {
        main {
          width: min(100% - 24px, 680px);
          padding: 32px 0 48px;
        }

        .grid,
        .manifesto {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero" aria-label="AI Engineering intro">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow">AI Engineering</p>
          <h1>Technology writing for people who build.</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="lede">
          Leituras sobre IA aplicada, sistemas, ferramentas, arquitetura e fundamentos técnicos
          para quem quer contexto suficiente para estudar melhor e decidir com mais clareza.
        </p>
        <div class="manifesto">
          <div>Software engineering com menos ruído e mais julgamento técnico.</div>
          <div>IA aplicada colocada ao lado de arquitetura, confiabilidade e entrega real.</div>
          <div>Guias, labs e estudos de caso para continuar depois da leitura.</div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid" aria-label="Language editions">
        {options.map((option) => (
          <article class="card">
            <img src={option.image} alt={option.title} loading="lazy" />
            <div class="copy">
              <h2>{option.title}</h2>
              <p>{option.description}</p>
              <a href={option.href} data-locale-link={option.locale}>{option.cta}</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </section>

      <div class="footer-note">
        Escolha um idioma, abra a matéria principal e use o restante do acervo para aprofundar o tema, praticar no browser ou observar decisões em projetos reais.
      </div>
    </main>

    <script is:inline>
      document.querySelectorAll('[data-locale-link]').forEach((link) => {
        link.addEventListener('click', () => {
          try {
            localStorage.setItem('preferredLocale', link.getAttribute('data-locale-link'));
          } catch {}
        });
      });
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
